<h4 id="what-we-know-about-tradingview-blackfriday-sales">What we know about TradingView Blackfriday sales</h4>

<p>We predict TradingView Black Friday deals based on data from <a href="#past2019-tradingview">2019</a>, <a href="#past2018-tradingview">2018</a> and <a href="#past2017">2017</a> Black Friday sales.</p>

<p>Every year, TradingView opens their Black Friday sale for the full Black Friday week (Monday - Sunday).</p>

<p>They typically give <strong>between 40% and 60%</strong> discount on their yearly paid plans. TradingView always runs the same sale offer through both Black Friday and Cyber Monday.</p>

<p>There is no difference in the TradingView Black Friday deal and the TradingView Cyber Monday deal.</p>

<p>Year on year, the Black Friday sale deals have been getting a tad better as the competition keeps popping up for TradingView.</p>

